Titolo: Donald Trump's Real Estate Tycoon

Anno: 2002

Descrizione: Donald Trump's Real Estate Tycoon is a business simulation game developed by RedCap and published by Activision Value. It was released for Microsoft Windows on November 7, 2002. It was later published in Europe by Xplosiv on September 3, 2004. On October 20, 2004, Activision Value published a version of the game that was developed by Airborne Entertainment for J2ME and BREW-enabled mobile phones, as well as the N-Gage QD. It was named after American businessman Donald Trump, who also provided his voice for both versions of the game.